WEBVTT

01:50.560 --> 01:52.640
Thank you for trusting me,

01:53.120 --> 01:54.920
but I'm going to disappoint you.

01:55.800 --> 01:57.200
I did copy from Meng.

02:04.360 --> 02:05.490
That's impossible.

02:11.720 --> 02:12.980
Don't call my parents.

02:14.040 --> 02:14.920
I'll write it.

02:16.120 --> 02:17.520
You've completely humiliated me.

02:17.520 --> 02:20.650
The parents of the bottom ten students will be called in.

02:22.040 --> 02:24.040
Sir, I won't waste words.

02:24.320 --> 02:26.380
Just tell me how you want to punish me.

02:29.160 --> 02:30.200
Go, go, go.

02:33.000 --> 02:33.680
Blockhead.

02:49.200 --> 02:50.920
It really is his handwriting.

02:55.720 --> 02:56.920
You are Alpha,

02:57.360 --> 02:59.760
but you disrespect your opponent too much.

03:04.080 --> 03:05.540
Will you ever cheat again?

03:07.280 --> 03:09.360
Mom, I won't.

03:09.760 --> 03:11.880
Why can't you behave?

03:18.480 --> 03:20.400
Thanks for your trust, everyone.

03:22.040 --> 03:23.640
But I have to disappoint you.

03:24.640 --> 03:26.200
I did copy from Meng.

03:30.640 --> 03:32.960
Why can't I figure him out anymore?

03:34.320 --> 03:34.960
No.

03:35.760 --> 03:37.520
I can't ask him so bluntly.

03:38.000 --> 03:39.260
I need to think of a way.

03:48.040 --> 03:48.920
Ruirui is here.

03:50.560 --> 03:51.620
Morning, Qingyun.

03:51.880 --> 03:54.560
Why did you call me here so early on a weekend?

03:57.600 --> 03:59.460
You're up to no good. I'm leaving.

04:00.440 --> 04:02.440
Someone promised me before

04:02.800 --> 04:05.680
that he would improve his rank as much as I did.

04:06.200 --> 04:08.480
Even though I didn't do well this time,

04:08.800 --> 04:11.520
he actually admitted to cheating.

04:12.760 --> 04:13.720
I think

04:14.280 --> 04:16.959
it's time for him to keep his promise

04:17.160 --> 04:18.440
and learn his lesson.

04:19.200 --> 04:20.279
In the next exam,

04:20.399 --> 04:21.839
however much you improve your rank,

04:21.839 --> 04:23.570
I'll improve mine just as much.

04:23.640 --> 04:24.320
Dare to bet?

04:24.400 --> 04:25.330
What if you lose?

04:25.760 --> 04:27.960
If I lose, I'll do whatever you want.

04:28.440 --> 04:29.560
If you lose,

04:29.840 --> 04:32.370
how about you do a handstand and eat Luosifen?

04:32.480 --> 04:33.720
If that's not enough,

04:34.720 --> 04:36.960
we'll be sisters from then on.

04:37.480 --> 04:39.280
You'll be my bestie. Do you dare?

04:41.840 --> 04:43.400
I'm so sleepy. I'm going back.

04:43.400 --> 04:44.200
No, you...

04:48.440 --> 04:51.440
Yuanbao, my mom spanked me.

04:51.560 --> 04:52.920
It still hurts.

05:31.560 --> 05:33.020
No, I really can't do this.

05:35.480 --> 05:36.800
I won't force you.

05:36.880 --> 05:38.440
Let's just be besties.

05:40.920 --> 05:42.240
Don't move.

05:44.640 --> 05:46.840
Do you think something is missing here?

05:47.159 --> 05:49.090
I think you can make it darker here.

05:52.400 --> 05:53.720
If I draw it like this,

05:53.840 --> 05:55.520
does it look like the one in the magazine?

05:55.520 --> 05:56.360
Hey, hey.

05:56.840 --> 05:58.840
You are not acting like besties.

05:59.200 --> 06:01.660
You are clearly trying to kill your brother.

06:02.760 --> 06:03.720
Then tell me.

06:03.960 --> 06:06.220
Why are you and Gong Yu so close recently?

06:07.040 --> 06:09.120
Weren't you two fighting before?

06:10.040 --> 06:12.300
We got to know each other after fighting.

06:12.360 --> 06:14.420
We laughed it off and became friends.

06:16.040 --> 06:19.160
How can you, someone who can't even recite a poem,

06:19.400 --> 06:21.200
show off your literary skills here?

06:21.200 --> 06:23.680
Tell me, how did you and Gong Yu get together?

06:27.280 --> 06:28.880
Yuanbao meant to ask,

06:29.080 --> 06:32.800
how you and Gong Yu got on good terms.

06:33.880 --> 06:36.760
Girls don't understand things between us boys.

06:37.640 --> 06:39.480
What's wrong with boys?

06:39.800 --> 06:40.880
Can't girls know about

06:40.880 --> 06:42.280
things between boys?

06:42.360 --> 06:43.040
No.

06:43.560 --> 06:46.159
Why do you have so many questions today?

06:46.760 --> 06:50.080
He's now complaining that girls ask too many questions.

06:50.480 --> 06:52.040
No. That's not what I meant.

06:52.120 --> 06:52.680
I mean,

06:52.760 --> 06:53.240
why are your questions today

06:53.240 --> 06:54.400
all so weird?

06:56.000 --> 07:00.000
Now he's complaining that girls are weird.

07:03.680 --> 07:04.800
Wait.

07:06.160 --> 07:07.040
I'll tell you.

07:07.120 --> 07:08.250
I'll tell you, okay?

07:10.520 --> 07:11.200
We

07:11.400 --> 07:13.160
almost got into a fight last time.

07:13.160 --> 07:13.760
And then,

07:14.880 --> 07:15.760
and then?

07:17.520 --> 07:18.240
And then,

07:18.920 --> 07:19.520
No.

07:20.040 --> 07:21.170
I still can't say it.

07:21.720 --> 07:22.480
Spit it out.

07:23.680 --> 07:24.440
Then,

07:24.880 --> 07:25.640
we...

07:25.760 --> 07:26.880
Well, between men,

07:26.960 --> 07:29.090
it's really from blows to friendship.

07:29.600 --> 07:30.760
Still not telling, right?

07:30.760 --> 07:33.090
I'll show you what you look like right now.

07:43.360 --> 07:44.440
You two fairies.

07:46.960 --> 07:48.320
Can I still

07:49.680 --> 07:51.080
go back and eat Luosifen?

08:02.600 --> 08:04.280
Ruirui, what are you doing?

08:04.760 --> 08:07.560
Your school hunk is solving a difficult question.

08:07.960 --> 08:10.020
What nonsense are you talking about?

08:11.520 --> 08:12.600
It's been so long.

08:12.720 --> 08:15.080
The weekly challenge question hasn't been solved yet.

08:15.080 --> 08:16.080
Can he do it?

08:16.280 --> 08:17.520
He must be new.

08:17.680 --> 08:18.960
I haven't seen him before.

08:18.960 --> 08:20.840
But this is obviously a physics competition question.

08:20.840 --> 08:22.360
Even the seniors can't answer it.

08:22.360 --> 08:24.420
He's overestimating his abilities.

08:26.280 --> 08:27.360
Class 20, Grade 10.

08:27.440 --> 08:28.480
Tian Yong's class.

08:28.480 --> 08:29.600
Would he send

08:29.720 --> 08:31.920
the answers to his classmates himself?

08:32.240 --> 08:33.559
Such a tasteless thing,

08:33.559 --> 08:34.960
neither our Mr. Tian

08:35.120 --> 08:36.960
nor the students of Class 20, Grade 10,

08:36.960 --> 08:38.120
would stoop so low to do.

08:38.120 --> 08:38.919
Exactly.

08:44.920 --> 08:47.280
I really envy him for being so smart.

08:47.440 --> 08:50.160
I mean, not only is he smart,

08:50.240 --> 08:51.040
but he's also handsome

08:51.040 --> 08:52.440
and has great character.

08:52.480 --> 08:56.080
He's practically the perfect male lead from a novel.

09:01.560 --> 09:02.600
This is...

09:02.960 --> 09:05.160
I bought too much breakfast. Have this.

09:21.760 --> 09:22.600
Mr. Tian,

09:22.800 --> 09:23.930
you're just in time.

09:24.040 --> 09:25.240
Let me introduce you.

09:25.560 --> 09:26.640
This is the new teacher,

09:26.640 --> 09:29.500
Ms. Xu Manli, who is taking over Mr. Zou's position.

09:34.720 --> 09:37.040
Ms. Xu, nice to meet you.

09:37.320 --> 09:38.450
Nice to meet you too.

09:41.040 --> 09:43.360
Mr. Liu, you're just in time.

09:43.800 --> 09:45.000
Let me introduce you.

09:47.840 --> 09:48.760
I... I know.

09:49.360 --> 09:52.160
You must be the new teacher taking Mr. Zou's place.

09:52.160 --> 09:53.220
My name is Xu Manli.

09:54.040 --> 09:56.760
Ms. Xu, nice to meet you.

09:57.600 --> 09:58.200
Hello.

09:58.800 --> 09:59.920
Well, Ms. Xu,

10:00.040 --> 10:02.080
what are your hobbies after work?

10:02.520 --> 10:03.800
I like working out,

10:03.840 --> 10:05.840
and occasionally watching movies.

10:06.320 --> 10:07.800
Then we're not only colleagues,

10:07.800 --> 10:10.000
but I'm sure we'll be good friends.

10:10.760 --> 10:11.920
Yes, definitely.

10:13.600 --> 10:15.000
You guys go ahead with your work.

10:15.000 --> 10:17.120
I'll show Ms. Xu around the school some more.

10:17.120 --> 10:17.450
Okay.

10:17.480 --> 10:17.920
Okay.

10:18.120 --> 10:18.560
Bye.

10:18.960 --> 10:19.360
Bye.

10:19.440 --> 10:21.440
Ms. Xu, call me if you need anything.

10:21.960 --> 10:23.480
Go!

10:25.320 --> 10:26.320
Go!

10:26.360 --> 10:27.240
Okay.

10:27.760 --> 10:29.280
Go!

10:32.400 --> 10:33.120
Okay.

10:36.000 --> 10:36.600
Go!

10:39.960 --> 10:42.240
Oh my god, Meng Jingu actually plays basketball!

10:42.240 --> 10:43.320
How is he good at everything?

10:43.320 --> 10:45.320
I heard good students are good at everything.

10:45.320 --> 10:46.650
They are well-rounded.

10:48.000 --> 10:50.200
I don't think he's as handsome as Gong Yu.

10:50.200 --> 10:54.120
Go!

10:56.320 --> 10:58.480
Go!

11:02.560 --> 11:04.120
Go!

11:04.200 --> 11:05.880
Meng Jingu is so handsome.

11:06.920 --> 11:09.520
Not only is he a good student from a good family,

11:09.520 --> 11:12.240
he's exactly like the male lead in a TV drama.

11:13.000 --> 11:14.840
Did you see his sneakers?

11:14.960 --> 11:15.800
They are so expensive.

11:15.800 --> 11:17.400
The point is, they're hard to buy.

11:17.400 --> 11:20.400
Good-looking people really do look good in anything.

11:21.440 --> 11:23.720
You guys don't know how to look. Gong Yu is more handsome.

11:23.720 --> 11:25.760
You don't understand the charm of a sports student.

11:25.760 --> 11:28.120
Look at his well-defined muscle lines.

11:28.200 --> 11:29.920
He's absolutely gorgeous.

11:30.320 --> 11:31.200
Meng Jingu is handsome.

11:31.200 --> 11:31.800
Gong Yu is handsome.

11:31.800 --> 11:32.360
Meng Jingu is handsome.

11:32.360 --> 11:33.360
Gong Yu.

11:34.360 --> 11:37.120
Mutou always used to snatch my water after playing basketball.

11:37.120 --> 11:39.400
I'll go and try offering it to him later.

11:40.680 --> 11:41.920
Go!

11:46.840 --> 11:47.480
Go!

12:05.560 --> 12:07.240
Let's go. Bring them some water.

12:07.240 --> 12:08.000
Let's go.

12:17.160 --> 12:17.880
That three-pointer was great.

12:17.880 --> 12:20.000
Not bad, that three-pointer just now.

12:20.000 --> 12:22.000
More importantly, the center is also very important.

12:22.000 --> 12:22.930
Very important.

12:24.000 --> 12:25.080
Jingu.

12:25.600 --> 12:27.760
Bro, your layup just now was so cool.

12:28.280 --> 12:29.800
We ran into Qingjun.

12:30.000 --> 12:31.920
Everyone knows his skills are crazy.

12:31.920 --> 12:32.920
I feel like he could make a three-pointer

12:32.920 --> 12:34.380
even with his eyes closed.

12:34.440 --> 12:35.160
Well,

12:35.520 --> 12:36.880
there's no shame in losing to him.

12:36.880 --> 12:38.000
A loss is a loss.

12:43.440 --> 12:44.040
Bro.

12:56.200 --> 12:57.560
There's no shame in losing to him.

12:57.560 --> 12:58.520
A loss is a loss.

12:59.280 --> 13:00.340
You must remember,

13:00.520 --> 13:03.080
the world only remembers the first place.

13:03.400 --> 13:04.520
The second place and the last place

13:04.520 --> 13:05.720
will equally be forgotten by the world.

13:05.720 --> 13:07.580
There's no shame in losing to him.

13:07.960 --> 13:08.800
No shame.

13:22.080 --> 13:23.810
You think my questions are easy

13:23.840 --> 13:25.300
and you dare to provoke me.

13:27.960 --> 13:28.760
Alpha.

13:29.960 --> 13:32.400
I underestimated you today.

13:33.160 --> 13:34.200
From now on,

13:34.520 --> 13:36.880
you are the rival who motivates me to improve.

13:36.880 --> 13:38.000
Don't let me down.

13:50.200 --> 13:52.320
I just discussed it with the class monitor.

13:52.320 --> 13:53.580
In today's study hall,

13:53.640 --> 13:55.840
our group will hold a quiz competition.

13:56.000 --> 13:57.530
We'll compete using dares.

13:58.120 --> 13:58.920
Dares?

13:59.600 --> 14:02.520
Does the loser have to go bungee jumping or something?

14:02.520 --> 14:03.680
Not bungee jumping.

14:03.800 --> 14:04.840
We'll draw lots to decide

14:04.840 --> 14:07.240
the punishment for whoever answers wrong.

14:07.280 --> 14:08.320
There are ten of us.

14:08.320 --> 14:09.880
Each writes down a punishment,

14:09.880 --> 14:11.540
and then we mix them together.

14:11.560 --> 14:12.560
The student who answers incorrectly

14:12.560 --> 14:14.280
will randomly pick a punishment from the pile.

14:14.280 --> 14:16.120
What if someone with bad intentions

14:16.120 --> 14:17.780
writes down the punishment as

14:17.920 --> 14:19.280
eating shit?

14:21.120 --> 14:22.520
How is your brain

14:22.560 --> 14:23.760
wired so weirdly?

14:24.400 --> 14:26.530
We won't write anything that extreme.

14:26.760 --> 14:27.760
Can I opt out?

14:27.920 --> 14:29.450
Punishment isn't the goal.

14:29.600 --> 14:31.960
The goal is to use this entertaining method

14:31.960 --> 14:33.560
to encourage everyone to do the exercises.

14:33.560 --> 14:34.760
I personally suggest

14:34.800 --> 14:36.320
that since you joined our group,

14:36.320 --> 14:37.780
it's best to participate.

14:42.640 --> 14:43.640
It's no big deal.

14:43.840 --> 14:44.970
Just join in for fun.

14:45.880 --> 14:46.640
Alright.

14:47.320 --> 14:49.050
Pretend I didn't say anything.

14:49.080 --> 14:50.140
Then it's settled.

14:50.640 --> 14:51.440
No problem.

14:52.400 --> 14:54.280
I don't know what this guy

14:54.360 --> 14:55.520
has up his sleeve.

15:00.640 --> 15:01.920
Based on the recent changes,

15:01.920 --> 15:03.050
the results are out.

15:03.400 --> 15:04.080
Besides me,

15:04.320 --> 15:05.720
the students who got everything right are

15:05.720 --> 15:06.440
Gao Jingyi

15:06.920 --> 15:07.720
and Xing Yaqi.

15:08.040 --> 15:10.320
The rest of you, please draw lots.

15:17.400 --> 15:18.160
Boring.

15:21.840 --> 15:23.840
My God, who wrote this?

15:24.040 --> 15:26.120
Sing the "Three Character Classic" to the tune of "Nunchucks."

15:26.120 --> 15:27.780
How am I supposed to sing that?

15:28.640 --> 15:29.560
You have to accept your loss.

15:29.560 --> 15:30.400
Don't try to cheat.

15:30.400 --> 15:32.160
Cut the crap and hurry up.

15:34.720 --> 15:35.480
I'm singing.

15:36.920 --> 15:39.050
Men at their birth are naturally good.

15:39.720 --> 15:42.960
Their natures are much the same, their habits become widely different.

15:42.960 --> 15:44.520
If not taught, their nature will deteriorate.

15:44.520 --> 15:46.160
Wind and water rising,

15:47.840 --> 15:49.440
upright spirit.

15:51.240 --> 15:52.680
Don't laugh, guys.

15:58.720 --> 16:00.360
I really want to ask,

16:00.720 --> 16:02.400
the student who wrote this note,

16:02.400 --> 16:03.480
do you

16:04.080 --> 16:05.840
have a grudge against me?

16:06.480 --> 16:08.760
Are you trying to kill me?

16:10.240 --> 16:11.120
What does it say?

16:11.120 --> 16:12.200
Yell,

16:12.760 --> 16:16.240
"Tian Yong, I want to fight you one-on-one."

16:19.440 --> 16:20.360
Tian Yong,

16:21.920 --> 16:23.320
you're pretty handsome.

16:25.360 --> 16:26.080
Yuanbao,

16:26.280 --> 16:27.140
it's your turn.

16:33.440 --> 16:36.440
Before I do this punishment, I just want to say,

16:37.480 --> 16:39.740
don't let me find out who wrote this note.

16:41.160 --> 16:43.120
I am a pig. I am a pig. I am a pig.

16:49.520 --> 16:50.400
Mu Qingjun,

16:50.720 --> 16:52.580
do you really not know how to do it,

16:52.800 --> 16:54.730
or do you just want the punishment?

16:55.680 --> 16:57.440
If I don't know it, I don't know it.

16:57.440 --> 16:59.640
What, are you a roundworm in my stomach?

17:01.240 --> 17:02.900
Which of you wants to go first?

17:04.720 --> 17:05.800
What did you draw?

17:08.040 --> 17:10.440
"Tell a secret to the person opposite you."

17:11.800 --> 17:13.119
Come on, tell me.

17:23.800 --> 17:25.060
You can't tell anyone.

17:26.480 --> 17:28.600
Wait, what secret are you talking about?

17:28.600 --> 17:29.800
I told you it's a secret.

17:29.800 --> 17:31.930
Would it still be a secret if I told you?

17:36.920 --> 17:37.840
Students,

17:38.000 --> 17:39.040
Students,

17:39.320 --> 17:41.320
during this study hall before school ends,

17:41.320 --> 17:43.560
I would like to grandly introduce

17:43.840 --> 17:44.920
Ms. Xu Manli,

17:45.120 --> 17:46.800
our new English teacher.

17:46.840 --> 17:48.840
Please give her a round of applause.

17:48.920 --> 17:49.920
Hello, everyone.

17:50.120 --> 17:51.520
It's nice to meet you all.

17:51.840 --> 17:53.840
If you have any questions about English,

17:53.840 --> 17:55.320
feel free to ask me anytime.

17:55.320 --> 17:57.760
And I hope I can not only be your teacher,

17:57.840 --> 17:59.360
but also your friend.

17:59.480 --> 18:00.000
Okay.

18:00.600 --> 18:01.040
Welcome, Ms. Xu.

18:01.040 --> 18:02.080
Welcome, Ms. Xu.

18:02.280 --> 18:03.440
Welcome, Ms. Xu.

18:05.080 --> 18:07.320
Well, I won't delay your class.

18:07.360 --> 18:08.490
I'll be leaving now.

18:09.920 --> 18:11.000
Take care, Ms. Xu.

18:16.920 --> 18:18.120
What did you just say to him?

18:18.120 --> 18:19.160
Why did you blush?

18:21.880 --> 18:22.720
Blush?

18:23.680 --> 18:24.800
I didn't blush.

18:25.480 --> 18:27.080
Do you think I'm color blind?

18:27.080 --> 18:28.440
You were obviously blushing.

18:28.440 --> 18:30.170
Tell me. What did you say to him?

18:32.680 --> 18:33.920
A secret is a secret.

18:34.520 --> 18:36.380
If I tell you, is it still a secret?

18:40.400 --> 18:42.200
Well, I'll tell you a secret.

18:42.600 --> 18:44.200
Think of it as compensation.

18:44.280 --> 18:45.000
What is it?

18:48.400 --> 18:49.080
Actually,

18:50.000 --> 18:51.080
that note of yours

18:51.720 --> 18:52.720
was written by me.

18:54.160 --> 18:55.480
It was you!

18:55.760 --> 18:57.880
You are Zhu Bajie!

19:03.640 --> 19:04.880
It hurts.

19:05.240 --> 19:06.240
What's wrong? I...

19:06.240 --> 19:07.520
I didn't hit you hard.

19:08.200 --> 19:09.560
I feel like it's broken.

19:11.560 --> 19:12.520
Piggyback me.

19:13.680 --> 19:15.680
Mu Qingyun, are you playing with me?

19:15.680 --> 19:17.120
Get off. You're so heavy.

19:20.960 --> 19:21.920
I'm telling you.

19:22.120 --> 19:24.050
I don't think Gong Yu is that great.

19:24.360 --> 19:26.320
Not to mention stealing money and hitting girls,

19:26.320 --> 19:28.680
he hangs out with those sketchy people.

19:28.920 --> 19:30.720
Who did you hear that from?

19:31.200 --> 19:33.040
I just heard it from others.

19:33.480 --> 19:35.960
Don't be young and naive and get led astray by him.

19:35.960 --> 19:38.800
Otherwise, I'll go tell Auntie on you.

19:41.280 --> 19:42.520
Okay, okay.

19:43.000 --> 19:44.280
Lord Yuanbao is right.

19:45.680 --> 19:46.360
I say,

19:46.760 --> 19:48.840
why are you like a little dog lately,

19:49.160 --> 19:50.960
always biting him and not letting go?

19:50.960 --> 19:53.200
You're the little dog. Get out of here.

19:58.760 --> 19:59.760
Stop right there.

20:00.560 --> 20:03.240
Gong Yu has bad grades. He'll lead you astray.

20:03.600 --> 20:05.930
Did you hear me? Stop hanging out with him.

20:06.440 --> 20:07.120
Mutou.

20:07.480 --> 20:08.200
Gong Yu.

20:09.400 --> 20:10.080
Ruirui.

20:14.240 --> 20:16.640
Wouldn't Mutou and Ruirui become enemies?

20:17.560 --> 20:18.200
No way.

20:19.360 --> 20:20.280
It can't be like this.

20:20.280 --> 20:21.240
I'm doomed.

20:22.280 --> 20:24.480
I have to save Mutou as soon as possible.

20:30.600 --> 20:31.880
Why are you sighing?

20:32.600 --> 20:35.200
And you? You've been sighing all day.

20:35.320 --> 20:36.240
What's wrong with you?

20:36.240 --> 20:37.480
What else could it be?

20:37.840 --> 20:38.920
Because of Gong Yu.

20:40.120 --> 20:41.120
I think

20:41.600 --> 20:42.880
he likes the kind of

20:43.600 --> 20:44.560
cool

20:44.840 --> 20:46.320
and very loyal girls.

20:46.600 --> 20:48.530
Unfortunately, I'm not that type.

20:52.400 --> 20:54.860
I bought it, and you won't even give me a bite.

20:54.920 --> 20:56.920
Fine, you can eat it.

21:00.440 --> 21:01.360
Give it back.

21:06.080 --> 21:06.960
No, no.

21:07.640 --> 21:09.840
I absolutely can't watch him go astray.

21:10.080 --> 21:12.040
How sad would this aunt be?

21:12.200 --> 21:13.330
What if he really...

21:21.280 --> 21:23.640
Ruirui, I have an idea.

21:31.280 --> 21:32.880
Tell me, if we really get together,

21:32.880 --> 21:34.280
what should we call each other?

21:34.280 --> 21:36.480
Going by age, I'm your older brother.

21:36.920 --> 21:38.720
That won't work. I'd lose face.

21:38.840 --> 21:39.570
I don't care.

21:39.600 --> 21:41.600
If we're together, I want to be your older brother.

21:41.600 --> 21:42.680
Come on, let me hear you call me that.

21:42.680 --> 21:44.610
Get out of here. I'm older than you.

21:45.920 --> 21:46.560
No.

21:57.680 --> 21:59.480
Ruirui, I've thought about it.

21:59.960 --> 22:02.720
First of all, this matter must not be made public.

22:04.840 --> 22:05.680
Don't worry.

22:08.240 --> 22:10.600
Secondly, since we know about it,

22:10.760 --> 22:12.620
we absolutely cannot sit idly by.

22:14.120 --> 22:14.960
You're right.

22:15.360 --> 22:18.000
So we should come up with a plan,

22:18.480 --> 22:20.480
a way to have the best of both worlds.

22:21.040 --> 22:21.880
What plan?

22:22.040 --> 22:23.440
Let's go check the books.

22:23.640 --> 22:24.700
As the saying goes,

22:25.160 --> 22:27.280
Don't regret having no followers when going out,

22:27.280 --> 22:30.080
there are plenty of carriages and horses in books.

22:31.000 --> 22:32.730
You can even recite poetry now.

22:33.400 --> 22:35.840
Talent really is forced out.

22:40.880 --> 22:42.480
The first step to success.

22:44.840 --> 22:45.520
Come on.

22:49.600 --> 22:52.000
High School Student Mental Health Manual.

22:55.240 --> 22:56.720
Light Up Your Youth.

22:59.240 --> 23:01.640
Psychological Growth of Rebellious Boys.

23:04.200 --> 23:06.560
Wait, why did you buy me these books?

23:06.680 --> 23:08.340
I don't have a mental illness.

23:09.880 --> 23:12.080
I recently saw a very popular post

23:12.160 --> 23:13.640
online.

23:14.280 --> 23:16.000
It's about our adolescence.

23:16.560 --> 23:19.640
It said that a lack of family education

23:20.120 --> 23:22.120
will have a very serious impact.

23:22.920 --> 23:24.920
Especially in terms of psychology.

23:25.200 --> 23:29.040
It will cause inferiority, autism,

23:29.600 --> 23:31.260
depression, mania, and so on.

23:31.800 --> 23:33.760
Especially this

23:35.680 --> 23:36.560
about

23:37.600 --> 23:39.360
the correct

23:42.800 --> 23:45.760
sex education in adolescence.

23:48.600 --> 23:49.560
Sex

23:49.880 --> 23:50.920
education

23:51.320 --> 23:52.080
issues?

23:52.240 --> 23:54.280
Correct views on sex.

23:54.520 --> 23:55.450
What did you say?

23:56.440 --> 23:57.920
Correct views on sex.

23:58.440 --> 24:00.440
Xiong Yuanbao, are you crazy?

24:01.160 --> 24:02.290
Don't get worked up.

24:02.960 --> 24:04.720
I just...

24:05.400 --> 24:07.440
You've been talking weirdly these past few days.

24:07.440 --> 24:09.500
What on earth are you thinking about?

24:10.120 --> 24:11.760
Don't let your imagination run wild.

24:11.760 --> 24:14.040
I just want to help you establish the correct concepts.

24:14.040 --> 24:15.970
Then why did you buy me these books?

24:16.960 --> 24:17.820
Think about it.

24:18.320 --> 24:19.800
Uncle and Aunt

24:19.880 --> 24:21.540
are usually so busy with work.

24:21.680 --> 24:23.120
Grandma is getting old.

24:23.600 --> 24:24.680
Since you were little,

24:24.680 --> 24:26.640
no one has cared about your mental

24:27.360 --> 24:28.840
and

24:29.040 --> 24:31.920
men's health issues.

24:32.200 --> 24:34.800
I just wanted to make up for what you missed.

24:36.920 --> 24:39.000
My mental

24:40.160 --> 24:42.800
and men's health are perfectly fine.

24:43.160 --> 24:45.160
Stop worrying about me for nothing.

24:46.000 --> 24:47.800
And what are these trashy books?

24:48.160 --> 24:49.080
I'm going to show them to Grandma.

24:49.080 --> 24:50.880
Let her see that you don't study hard every day

24:50.880 --> 24:52.480
and only read this nonsense.

24:54.400 --> 24:55.200
Give it back.

24:55.280 --> 24:56.040
If you don't want it, fine.

24:56.040 --> 24:57.000
But showing it to Grandma?

24:57.000 --> 24:58.360
Are you trying to kill me?

24:58.360 --> 24:59.220
Then promise me

24:59.240 --> 25:00.080
you'll never read

25:00.080 --> 25:01.280
this nonsense again.

25:02.160 --> 25:03.320
I won't.

25:04.240 --> 25:05.960
Give it back if you don't want it.

25:05.960 --> 25:06.880
No way.

25:07.760 --> 25:09.840
This is a gift from Lord Yuanbao.

25:10.960 --> 25:12.420
If you dare bully me again,

25:12.600 --> 25:13.760
I'll show it to Grandma.

25:13.760 --> 25:14.960
You villain.

25:16.240 --> 25:16.970
Give it back!

25:17.520 --> 25:18.320
Give it back!

25:19.160 --> 25:19.840
Give it...

25:24.640 --> 25:26.040
I really didn't mean to.

25:26.720 --> 25:27.480
Are you okay?

25:27.480 --> 25:29.010
Should I call an ambulance?

25:30.480 --> 25:32.920
I think you just don't want me to be well.

25:34.200 --> 25:34.880
No.

25:35.000 --> 25:36.000
I'm sorry.

25:36.080 --> 25:37.640
I really didn't mean to.

26:08.240 --> 26:09.040
This weekend.

26:09.120 --> 26:11.240
Time: This weekend.

26:11.400 --> 26:12.960
Xitanghe Park.

26:13.280 --> 26:14.120
Okay, that works.

26:14.120 --> 26:15.840
Location: Xitanghe Park.

26:16.040 --> 26:16.600
Okay.

26:16.680 --> 26:18.480
Don't worry. I'll go right after playing basketball.

26:18.480 --> 26:21.000
They are meeting in private.

26:21.080 --> 26:21.840
Don't worry.

26:22.120 --> 26:22.640
For our first date,

26:22.640 --> 26:24.170
I definitely won't be late.

26:24.840 --> 26:25.720
First date?

26:25.960 --> 26:27.120
Late.

26:27.160 --> 26:28.480
Okay, it's a deal then.

26:29.080 --> 26:30.200
See you there.

26:42.160 --> 26:42.840
Mutou.

26:43.400 --> 26:44.040
What?

26:47.760 --> 26:48.840
Does it still hurt?

26:59.760 --> 27:00.760
I'm heading back.

27:11.360 --> 27:12.080
Ruirui.

27:12.800 --> 27:13.840
Plan A failed.

27:15.360 --> 27:17.200
I've been looking up information online these past two days

27:17.200 --> 27:19.000
and asking around.

27:19.280 --> 27:20.000
I think we can

27:20.000 --> 27:21.480
move on to the second step of the plan.

27:21.480 --> 27:23.080
Midterm exams are coming up.

27:23.200 --> 27:24.200
Let's make it quick.

27:24.200 --> 27:26.130
Let's try not to delay our studies.

27:27.080 --> 27:29.120
Step two to success. Let's go!

27:29.640 --> 27:30.360
Come on.

27:36.720 --> 27:37.960
What's meant to be will be.

27:37.960 --> 27:40.490
Stop overthinking and focus on your studies.

28:07.400 --> 28:08.040
Gong Yu.

28:09.200 --> 28:10.440
I have a friend

28:11.160 --> 28:12.960
who's really good at billiards.

28:13.240 --> 28:15.700
She asked me to play billiards this weekend.

28:15.840 --> 28:17.240
Are you interested

28:18.240 --> 28:19.040
in joining us?

28:19.200 --> 28:20.080
Not interested.

28:20.080 --> 28:22.200
I... I am.

28:25.520 --> 28:26.160
Gong Yu.

28:26.760 --> 28:28.600
We are in the same class.

28:28.840 --> 28:31.500
What's wrong with playing billiards together?

28:32.640 --> 28:34.040
Don't be so pretentious.

28:36.040 --> 28:37.970
Take it easy. You're going too far.

28:41.240 --> 28:42.200
Exactly.

28:42.640 --> 28:44.400
I mean,

28:44.720 --> 28:46.920
since we are in the same class,

28:47.560 --> 28:49.520
playing billiards together can

28:50.320 --> 28:51.850
enhance our relationship.

28:52.000 --> 28:53.080
Makes sense.

28:53.600 --> 28:54.280
Well,

28:54.360 --> 28:57.520
I heard you play billiards often.

28:58.040 --> 28:59.800
Since our Ruirui invited you,

29:00.040 --> 29:00.960
you should go.

29:02.160 --> 29:02.960
Are you full?

29:03.400 --> 29:04.200
Yes.

29:04.720 --> 29:06.280
I'm going to the sports equipment room.

29:06.280 --> 29:07.960
Let's go together. I have something to tell you.

29:07.960 --> 29:08.640
Okay.

29:09.520 --> 29:10.320
You can't go.

29:14.840 --> 29:15.920
Don't go.

29:16.600 --> 29:20.240
Brother Qingyun, stay and eat with me.

29:20.920 --> 29:22.200
Enjoy your meal.

29:22.280 --> 29:23.340
I'll be right back.

29:35.520 --> 29:38.760
Looks like our trick failed.

29:39.880 --> 29:41.280
I think so too.

29:42.040 --> 29:44.000
Why doesn't it seem to work?

29:45.000 --> 29:46.280
What's going on?

29:46.720 --> 29:48.480
Isn't this what the book says?

29:49.320 --> 29:51.160
What exactly went wrong?

29:51.680 --> 29:52.640
Yeah.

29:53.880 --> 29:55.560
What's wrong with you two today?

29:55.560 --> 29:57.040
What trick?

29:57.320 --> 29:58.720
Are you out of your minds?

29:59.360 --> 30:00.480
Just eat your food.

30:00.800 --> 30:01.520
Okay.

30:13.400 --> 30:14.040
Deskmate.

30:14.600 --> 30:16.330
Are you waiting for Mu Qingyun?

30:17.400 --> 30:18.080
By the way,

30:18.520 --> 30:19.960
I want my umbrella back.

30:22.560 --> 30:23.400
Okay, okay.

30:23.960 --> 30:25.490
I don't mean anything else.

30:25.560 --> 30:27.840
I just think giving an umbrella as a gift is bad luck.

30:27.840 --> 30:29.500
I'll give you something else.

30:30.160 --> 30:30.920
Yuanbao.

30:35.920 --> 30:39.400
We're already in a mutual help group, and you still get extra tutoring?

30:39.400 --> 30:40.600
Why don't you tutor me too?

30:40.600 --> 30:42.130
You don't need my tutoring.

30:42.720 --> 30:44.200
Deskmate, I'll go first.

30:44.520 --> 30:45.160
Goodbye.

30:45.800 --> 30:47.060
Bye, see you tomorrow.

30:48.080 --> 30:50.210
This kid actually knows some manners.

30:50.360 --> 30:52.160
What was he talking to you about?

30:52.560 --> 30:54.480
Nothing much, just saying hi.

31:06.800 --> 31:07.800
What time is it?

31:08.160 --> 31:10.040
Did they cancel their date?

31:10.920 --> 31:12.400
I'm sure he's at home.

31:12.800 --> 31:14.920
If their date is canceled today,

31:15.360 --> 31:17.720
that proves our mission is accomplished.

31:18.120 --> 31:20.520
When sisters unite, they are unstoppable.

31:21.560 --> 31:23.320
Do you remember

31:23.520 --> 31:25.080
their expressions after you said that?

31:25.080 --> 31:27.000
It was like a bolt from the blue.

31:27.040 --> 31:29.570
They were completely dumbstruck on the spot.

31:30.040 --> 31:31.760
There's no problem we can't solve.
